div.p: Transition colors Blue normal happy path Green success / Ack Red error / poison / ILLEGAL Purple dashed duplicate skip (Ack) Yellow milestone triggered Orange AMQP infrastructure event Key invariants prefetch=1: at most 1 in-flight msg per consumer goroutine All DB work (dedup + click + milestone) in ONE transaction Poison msgs Ack (never Nack) to prevent infinite requeue Publish failure is warn-only; tx.Commit still proceeds healthy flag read by /health; consumer pause HTTP 500
